flowchart TB
    U[User: Sarthi] --> M[main agent\nOrchestrator + Policy Gate]

    M --> O[Outline-first planner]
    O --> R[research agent]
    O --> C[coder agent]
    O --> T[tx agent]
    O --> J[janitor agent]

    subgraph SESSION_SANDBOX[Session-Scoped Sandboxes]
      R --> SR[(research sandbox)]
      C --> SC[(coder sandbox)]
    end

    subgraph AGENT_SANDBOX[Persistent Specialist Sandbox]
      T --> ST[(tx sandbox)]
    end

    J --> HOST[Host OS\nMonitoring/Cleanup]

    R --> CR[Crawlee-lite]
    R --> IF[InsightForge-lite\nmax 3 sub-queries]
    C --> RC[ReACT caps\nmax tools=5, reflect=3]
    T --> RT[Risk Tiers\nSAFE/CAUTION/ESCALATE]

    M --> SM[Task State Machine\nCREATED→RUNNING→DONE/FAILED]
    M --> WD[Watchdog pattern\n(Antfarm-style)]
    M --> AJ[JSONL Audit Trail\nrotated]

    MEM[Observer/Reflector Memory Loop\n(daily/weekly)] --> M
    SK[Chain Skill Packs\nHelius/Solana/Layr (phased)] --> T

    SR --> EXT[External APIs/Web]
    SC --> REPO[Repos/Toolchains]
    ST --> PAY[Payment rails (future)]

    SEC[(Secrets Store\n~/.openclaw/secrets)] --> R
    SEC --> C
    SEC --> T

